.nh 1 "The Dependency Maintenance Tool"
.LP
Aegis can place heavy demands on the dependency maintenance tool, so it
is important that you select an appropriate one.  This chapter talks
about what features a dependency maintenance tool requires, and gives
examples of how to use the various alternatives.
